{"tid":1492181,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Twitter之戰】籃球撚 係時候企出黎喇！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T17:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:13:04.000Z","uid":29900,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b25afff03819a61229e18cc5984f2b60ea2c56e7","tid":1492181,"uid":29900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"作為一個湖人球迷，<br />\n喺上年得知湖人今年pre season會喺深圳對上網隊，<br />\n呢個可能係我一生人 <br />\n唯一一次可以現場觀看自己深愛嘅球隊比賽嘅機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住不但可以見到Ingram、Lonzo <br />\n仲可以同Dlo團聚（而家就不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n果刻嘅心情真係興奮過打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係經過呢兩個月嘅抗爭 <br />\n香港人而家上大陸 <br />\n可能仲危險過半場放空Stephen Curry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 小弟已經係放棄左呢個完夢嘅機會八 九成架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雖然係咁</span><br />\n<br />\n眼見香港人嘅團結 同無限嘅創意運動<br />\n再加上俾上次波台手足喺大球場嘅活動啟發<br />\n我地籃球撚都係時候做d野喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">買左飛又有勇氣嘅ching可以去現場舉牌<br />\n但由於唔係主場同人數嘅關係 再加上NBA都奶奶地共(?)真係要三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正因為而家美國咁關注我哋香港<br />\n而籃球又係美國佬嘅運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上連登仔而家已經開發左新技能 &mdash; Twitter<br />\n千祈唔好以為Twitter 淨係用嚟對抗五毛有用<br />\n其實仲可以用黎直接message/tag世界各地嘅名人<br />\n而且 個效果可能超乎你想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國人最常用嘅social media就係Twitter <br />\n基本上你message/tag佢 <br />\n佢會睇到嘅機會都會比其他social media高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有唔少嘅明星、球星或者係名人<br />\n都好鍾意得閒喺Twitter 同普羅大眾交流下<br />\n（雖然大部份時間都係串鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但就係勝在佢哋敢發敢言 <br />\n我哋呢個行動先至有機會散播得更加廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講咗咁耐<br />\n係時候要講下呢個行動到底應該要做d咩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先你可以去Twitter當寫信咁<br />\ntag個球星 直接寫出我哋香港而家嘅局面<br />\n我地抗爭嘅理由 &rdquo;fight for democracy, fight for freedom&rdquo;（加插大量文宣、圖片同hashtag）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">個人主張 LeBron (@kingjames),AD(@AntDavis23), KD(@KDTrey35),同Kyrie(@KyrieIrving)<br />\n一嚟佢哋係超級球星，LBJ,KD同kyrie嚟過幾次香港<br />\n二來佢哋喺兩個月之後會去深圳打pre season嘅球員(KD傷左未必會跟隊去)</span><br />\n 講下自己本來好想去睇呢一場波<br />\n但因為中国嘅關係 去現場睇要冒好大嘅險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（Magic都係1個我認為有機會睇到同回應嘅傳奇球員）</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">個人來講我仲會試吓tag Kobe但覺得機會唔大</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總括來講就係希望 能夠令我哋鍾意嘅球星留意香港發生緊嘅事<br />\n如果佢哋retweet當然就更加好 <br />\n仲要俾佢哋知道我哋香港人高汁過班支那人好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爭取NBA Pre season 2021 Hong Kong series!!!!<br />\n#NBAHongKongSeries</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">歡迎討論除咗NBA球員之外 仲可以tag咩名人試下</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔 一齊Twitter遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e6e1ad1c29845e3572ab8bb354b65a34891eaa7","tid":1492181,"uid":29900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4000491b7e0d051ec42a09c7bb61f4b0051e9b9","tid":1492181,"uid":29900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"一齊喺Twitter同中意嘅球星交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405547b8eeb8b3c8e93f83c65b7fb87ce542f28e","tid":1492181,"uid":116434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53893b025769479170cf84f5148881c374375dfc","tid":1492181,"uid":224419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c13f851d560358328188f9a1c576ed5d184521","tid":1492181,"uid":169939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Hh1f2P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Hh1f2P.jpg&h=d3e73d48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UR5FwBa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUR5FwBa.jpg&h=d50714ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KAm0uv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KAm0uv.jpg&h=2c526271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3b856d5e0436f81a655ceb3d10a45dc7865e38","tid":1492181,"uid":29900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"教練 我好想去睇波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915480d211c0fef2632830158d45f8c19a19c27a","tid":1492181,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"好想去但真係唔敢去"},{"pid":"692f12334a36a25d67a985c1bf727e6646afbe66","tid":1492181,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"kuzma一直關注中"},{"pid":"848104788bc96981ba485d43c29efbbd6be2a395","tid":1492181,"uid":128569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"之前kuzma都有轉過關於香港既新聞"},{"pid":"9091ecb98c6ab2eed851faa8658c0ea5dc0cd0ef","tid":1492181,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89f0643e3bb7cc56bf393dc13cbf3e033ccdac0","tid":1492181,"uid":29900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"915480d211c0fef2632830158d45f8c19a19c27a","tid":1492181,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"好想去但真係唔敢去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"儲返幾年錢 去LA睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c191786495a8a2ba17759c8e3672933f2a92a985","tid":1492181,"uid":29900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"848104788bc96981ba485d43c29efbbd6be2a395","tid":1492181,"uid":128569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"之前kuzm